      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIG EASY AL (2) was below best last time finishing seventh at Q Lakeside, but prior to that had been racing well including a Mix 5 win two back at Q Lakeside. Can turn form around here. JUMPING JIVE (1) missed the frame last time out when fifth at this track from Box three (30.44) but draws same box here as latest win. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with four wins from five starts. Bold showing expected. GLEN'S WISH (8) started big odds last time but hit the ground running with a slick early split, giving a sight but fading out of it to finish sixth (19.81) at Q Lakeside over 352m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Warrants plenty of respect. CHA CHA KITTY (6) must be among the chances on the last run here.",
